    <h2>
      For one MSU student, nursing is a family affair
    </h2>

    <p class="slug">
      Morgan State’s nursing program recently received accreditation this year
      and admitted its largest cohort of students. Meet one of its rising stars
      and the mother who inspired her.
    </p>
    <hr class="class-6" />
    <p class="author">
      Oyin Adedoyin, Editor in Chief
    </p>
    <p class="date">
      October 16, 2020
    </p>
